Quickstrike:





Quickstrike slowly turned his head to Black Arachnia. He was already getting 
tired of waiting around for things to get done. He was a little bored. When 
the call for the stasis pod came, he'd come running.

He wrapped his arm around her waist, being still careful around her. He knew 
she could kill him, but it was easy going with this type of female. He had 
to watch her reactions and go with it when she didn't want to be bothered. 
But he was happy to know that she was back in the ranks of the Predacons.

"Say, uuh, sugar-bot, mind if ya take me on uh tour of th' base?" he softly 
said to her.
